kid Injection	kid: "../dev/null" → empty key, sign w/ ""	Sanitize/validate kid param
Weak Secret	secret=123456 brute-forced	32+ random bytes, env vars, never code
No Signature Check	jwt.decode() instead of verify()	Always verify(), never just decode
Missing Claims	No exp/iss/aud validation	Check exp < now, iss matches, aud correct
JWK/JKU Abuse	Attacker hosts own public key	Pin keys, validate JWK URLs, no remote fetch
Token Leakage	JWT in URL/logs → stolen	HTTPS only, short expiry, HttpOnly cookies